      <akn:section eId="sec_44_111_01">
        <akn:num>44-111.01</akn:num>
        <akn:heading>Insurance for Assisted Living Residences.</akn:heading>
<akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-111_01_a">
      <akn:num>(a)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>Each ALR shall carry insurance for at least the following:</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection><akn:subsection eId="subsec_44-111_01_b">
      <akn:num>(b)</akn:num>
      <akn:content><akn:p>If an ALR is not owned by the operator or manager, the operator or manager shall obtain proof of the owner’s premises liability coverage, such as a certificate of standard landlord coverage, or shall place the owner on the operator’s or manager’s policy as an additional named insured.</akn:p></akn:content>
    </akn:subsection>
      </akn:section>
